# DateRangePicker

The date range picker lets users select date range like a week with an interface that looks like a calendar and is just as straightforward to use.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/date-range-picker
```

```tsx
import { DateRangePicker } from '@ids-ts/date-range-picker';
```

